title: Mortgage Debt Outstanding by Type of Holder and Property: Individuals and Other Holders for Nonfarm and Nonresidential Properties (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Mortgage Debt Outstanding table is no longer being updated as of March 2020. Many of the series that were published in this table can be found in the Z1 Financial Accounts of the United States release. The Z1 equivalent of this series is the sum of BOGZ1FL643065505Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL643065505Q), BOGZ1FL213065503Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL213065503Q), BOGZ1FL223065545Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL223065545Q), BOGZ1FL573065505Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL573065505Q), BOGZ1FL613065503Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL613065503Q), BOGZ1FL153065505Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL153065505Q), BOGZ1FL103065503Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL103065503Q), BOGZ1FL113065503Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL113065503Q) and BOGZ1FL513065505Q (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BOGZ1FL513065505Q).

For further information, please refer to the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve System's Mortgage Debt Outstanding (http://www.federalreserve.gov/econresdata/releases/mortoutstand/current.htm).
